  "text": "We propose a new fusion rule based on wavelets for multiexposed images. Our approach differs from the simple summation of the detail sub-bands of input images in the method of Malik et al., [CITATION_1] in that we fuse the detail subbands with an adjusted contrast weight, and the details of fused images are enhanced to a different extent with an enhancement function.",
